{{define "content"}}
<nav class="cds-breadcrumb" aria-label="Breadcrumb"><a href="/admin/overview">Admin</a> / Restart</nav>
<h1 class="cds-h1">Restart</h1>
{{if .Notice}}<div class="cds-inline-notification cds-inline-notification--success" role="status">{{.Notice}}</div>{{end}}
<div class="cds-tile">
  <h2 class="cds-h2">Restart node</h2>
  <p>Restarting stops the node gracefully and lets the supervisor bring it back
  up with the persisted settings applied. In-flight crawls and searches are
  interrupted for a few seconds; durable queues resume where they left off.</p>
  <form method="post" action="/admin/restart" hx-boost="false">
    <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{.CSRF}}">
    <input type="hidden" name="target" value="node">
    <button class="cds-btn cds-btn--danger" type="submit">Restart node now</button>
  </form>
</div>
{{if .CrawlerRestart}}
<div class="cds-tile">
  <h2 class="cds-h2">Restart crawlers</h2>
  <p>Signal every connected crawler to shut down gracefully and be brought back
  up by its supervisor. The command reaches each worker over the gRPC control
  plane on its next heartbeat; the node keeps running. Leased orders return to
  the durable queue and resume once the worker reconnects.</p>
  <form method="post" action="/admin/restart" hx-boost="false">
    <input type="hidden" name="csrf_token" value="{{.CSRF}}">
    <input type="hidden" name="target" value="crawler">
    <button class="cds-btn cds-btn--danger" type="submit">Restart crawlers now</button>
  </form>
</div>
{{end}}
{{end}}

